name: Only one level (ZeNavalheira)
description:
Yeah... I will be fair with you. I do not have a lot of money... I never did, and I never will. I wanted to play the Nintendo Switch's Mario Maker because it brings me back to the memory of the good old times. Since I cannot buy it, maybe I can do my one version... and this was the result. A really hard level just for me. You can reach the final, I tried several times... sometimes I actually finished it. Super annoying kinky music with a subtle way of calling you falling t*rd -> maybe you will get the reference : )

Move : arrow keys or wasd
Jump: space

Kudos for https://kenney.itch.io for the amazing sprites.
Kudos for https://about.me/ken.snyder for the music

Enjoy!
